&lt;p&gt;Is this a duplicate of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17927&quot; title=&quot;sanity test_119e: FAIL: trivial unaligned dio failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-17927&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-17927&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;?&lt;/p&gt;

